  "abstract": "The Board is proposing amendments to Regulation D, Reserve Requirements of Depository Institutions, to move from the current system of contemporaneous reserve maintenance for institutions that are weekly reporters to a system under which reserves are maintained on a lagged basis by such institutions. Under a lagged reserve maintenance system, the reserve maintenance period for a weekly reporter will begin 30 days after the beginning of a reserve computation period. Under the current system, the ",
